<br>
Crucible of Escape!<br>
<br>
It's a right clickable, unlimited charge item with the Lessor Succor Spell... same cast time as the druid spell (and the same as the wizard lesser evac).  Just open up your inventory, make sure the crucible is in a general inventory slot, and click away... 10 seconds later you and your group is out of there.<br>
<br>
On sale in the bazaar whenever I'm there.<br>
<br>
Also, you folks might find these interesting...<br>
<br>
Golden Idol of Ersollisi Marr 8 ac 5 wis 5 chr 40 mana 9 disease<br>
Golden Idol of Bristlebane 7 ac 9 str 5 dex 5 agi<br>
Golden Idol of Karana 4 ac 4 sta 5 wis 40 mana <br>
Golden Idol of Tunare 4 ac 5 wis 40 mana 6 disease 6 poison<br>
Golden Idol of Rallos Zek 10 ac 9 str 5 sta 20 hp<br>
Golden Idol of Solosek Ro 4 ac 6 int 40 mana 9 fire save<br>
<br>
All are range slot diety specific.  Other golden idols for any diety also available.  All golden idols are 1500pp if in stock, 1kpp plus five imbued gems of your diety if not in stock.<br>
<br>
And Faith and Spiritstones... unlimited charges gate to Birth City for clerics and shamen... clerics go to their starting guilds, and shamen to just outside their cities.  Level 51 and up, 30 second cast time, for 3500pp.<br>
<br>
Jarkell Ravensteel<br>
